OL,3,C'Utterly unique' Bronze Age hoard
OL,4,Csaved for the nation
OL,6,FAn "utterly unique" hoard of hundreds
OL,7,Fof Bronze Age items discovered by a
OL,8,Fmetal detectorist in the Scottish
OL,9,FBorders has been saved for the nation
OL,10,Fafter it was acquired by the national
OL,11,Fmuseum.
OL,13,FThe Peebles Hoard, which dates from
OL,14,F1000-800 BCE and was found by metal
OL,15,Fdetectorist Mariusz Stepien in 2020,
OL,16,Fcomprises more than 500 bronze and
OL,17,Forganic pieces that had lain
OL,18,Fundisturbed for more than 3,000 years.
