OL,3,C'Utterly unique' Bronze Age hoard
OL,4,Csaved for the nation
OL,6,FThe hoard has now been acquired by
OL,7,FNational Museums Scotland, and efforts
OL,8,Fare under way to secure funding for
OL,9,Fthe continued research and
OL,10,Fconservation of this "exceptional"
OL,11,Ffind.
OL,13,FMatthew Knight, senior curator of
OL,14,Fprehistory at National Museums
OL,15,FScotland, said: "The Peebles Hoard is
OL,16,Fexceptional, an utterly unique
OL,17,Fdiscovery that rewrites our
OL,18,Funderstanding of both Bronze Age
OL,19,Fcommunities in Scotland and our
OL,20,Fprehistoric international connections.
