OL,4,Csaved for the nation
OL,6,F"Thanks to the diligence of the
OL,7,Ffinder, expertise of colleagues at the
OL,8,FTreasure Trove Unit and National
OL,9,FMuseums Scotland, and the generosity
OL,10,Fof the team at the -VIS X-ray Imaging
OL,11,FCentre, University of Southampton, we
OL,12,Fhave made significant progress.
OL,14,F"However, more funding is critical to
OL,15,Fcontinue our conservation and
OL,16,Fresearch, to preserve the hoard for
OL,17,Ffuture generations and uncover the
OL,18,Fstories of Scotland's ancient past."
