OL,3,C'Utterly unique' Bronze Age hoard
OL,4,Csaved for the nation
OL,6,FAfter being reported as a Treasure
OL,7,FTrove to National Museum Scotland the
OL,8,Fhoard was excavated from the ground in
OL,9,Fa single block of earth, which was
OL,10,Fthen further excavated and analysed
OL,11,Funder laboratory conditions.
OL,13,FThis included the entire block of
OL,14,Fearth being CT scanned at a specialist
OL,15,Fimaging facility at the University of
OL,16,FSouthampton, which captured details of
OL,17,Fthe internal structure of the hoard,
OL,18,Fand relationships between items in
OL,19,Ftheir original context.
