OL,6,F"CT-scanning the hoard was certainly a
OL,7,Fbig challenge due to the scale of the
OL,8,Fhoard block, but we relished the
OL,9,Fopportunity to bring our engineering
OL,10,Fskills to successfully support this
OL,11,Fresearch on such an exceptional
OL,12,Fhistorical find."
OL,14,FNational Museums Scotland is now
OL,15,Flaunching a fundraising campaign to
OL,16,Fsupport the costs of conserving the
OL,17,Fhoard, and of unlocking its research
OL,18,Fpotential.
